# custom-studio-app — project conventions

- **Root of the Next app**: this directory (`custom-studio-app/`). Run `npm run dev`, `npm run build`, `npm run lint` from here.
- **Design system (full detail)**: `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` — fonts, `--studio-*` vs semantic tokens, motion, file placement.
- **Next.js 16**: prefer official in-repo docs when behavior is unclear; breaking changes vs older Next are noted in `AGENTS.md`.
- **Imports**: use `@/` aliases from `components.json` (`@/components`, `@/components/ui`, `@/lib`, `@/hooks`).
- **Scope**: keep changes focused on the task; match existing patterns in neighboring files (naming, `cn()`, token usage).
